summary: Alters the existing shore water wave sound loop by adding seagull cries (and additional distant waves). Subtle and pleasing effect on the atmosphere.
descriptionHtml:
Ambient Seagulls (Ambient Gulls)

Alters the existing shore water wave sound loop by adding seagull cries (and additional distant waves). Subtle and pleasing effect on the atmosphere.

Use mod manager or manually place the supplied data folder into your Skyrim directory data/sound/fx/amb/water/exterior/coast/waves/

amb_water_exterior_coast_waves_01lp.wav
amb_water_exterior_coast_waves_02lp.wav
amb_water_exterior_coast_waves_03lp.wav
author: Tricolour
